MNEMONIST-EXTRAVERSION.description:
[gold]Psych{IfUpgraded:show:+|}[/gold] {Humors:diff()}
Deal damage equal to thrice the number of [gold]Humors[/gold] in your [gold]Draw Pile[/gold].{InCombat:
(Deals {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage.)|}

MNEMONIST-NOTE_TO_SELF.description:
Exhaust ALL your [gold]Status[/gold] cards.
At the start of your turn, gain half that amount of [blue]Memory[/blue].{InCombat:
(Gains {Memory:diff()} [blue]Memory[/blue] each turn.)|}

MNEMONIST-OBLIVIOUS.description:
Spend all your [blue]Memory[/blue], gain twice that much [gold]Block[/gold].
For every {PerEnergy:diff()}, gain {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} and draw a card.{InCombat:
(Gains {CalculatedBlock:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].)|}

MNEMONIST-QUICK_TO_RECALL.description:
Exhaust ALL {IfUpgraded:show:your [gold]Status[/gold] cards|[gold]Status[/gold] cards in your [gold]Draw Pile[/gold]}.
Gain 1 [blue]Memory[/blue] for each.{InCombat:
(Gains {Memory:diff()} [blue]Memory[/blue].)|}

MNEMONIST-WEIGHT_OF_MEMORY.description:
Gain {Memory:diff()} [blue]Memory[/blue].
Deal damage equal to twice your [blue]Memory[/blue]. If [gold]Fatal[/gold], permanently increase this card's [blue]Memory[/blue] by {Increase:diff()}.{InCombat:
(Deals {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage.)|}
